OL,3,C999 call released after man steals car
OL,4,Cwith elderly blind woman inside
OL,6,FA horrifying 999 call has been
OL,7,Freleased by police after a man stole a
OL,8,Fcar with an elderly blind woman with
OL,9,Fdementia still inside.
OL,11,FDavid Stephenson, 51, has been jailed
OL,12,Ffor more than eight years after being
OL,13,Ffound guilty of kidnap, theft of motor
OL,14,Fvehicle, dangerous driving and driving
OL,15,Fwithout a license.
OL,17,FHe jumped into a car, which was still
OL,18,Frunning to keep the 89-year-old
OL,19,Fdisabled mother warm while her
OL,20,Fdaughter headed to the shops in on 6
OL,21,FJanuary 2024.
