OL,3,C999 call released after man steals car
OL,4,Cwith elderly blind woman inside
OL,6,FAfter releasing her car was gone, the
OL,7,Fvictim's daughter made a panicked call
OL,8,Fto 999 for help.
OL,10,FIn footage shared by , following
OL,11,FStephenson's sentencing, the woman is
OL,12,Fheard saying: "I've gone to the shop
OL,13,Fto pick some slippers up for my mum
OL,14,Fand I've come back and my car's gone
OL,15,Fwith my mum. My mum's in the car."
OL,17,FThe terrified caller goes on to say:
OL,18,F"They've took her, they've took my car
OL,19,Fand my mum. She's disabled and she's
OL,20,Fblind and she's got dementia.
