OL,3,C999 call released after man steals car
OL,4,Cwith elderly blind woman inside
OL,6,F"My mum's in the car, what will they
OL,7,Fdo with her?! What will they do with
OL,8,Fher?! What will they do with my mum?
OL,9,FOh my god, what will they do with my
OL,10,Fmum?"
OL,12,FUnfazed by the fact a vulnerable woman
OL,13,Fwas in the passenger seat, Stephenson
OL,14,Fled officers on a pursuit across
OL,15,FAshton-under-Lyne, clocking speeds of
OL,16,Fup to 66mph.
OL,18,FPolice were thankfully able to bring
OL,19,Fthe car to a safe stop, detain
OL,20,FStephenson, and reunite the victim
OL,21,Fwith her daughter.
