OL,3,C999 call released after man steals car
OL,4,Cwith elderly blind woman inside
OL,6,FChief Inspector Matt Jackson from our
OL,7,FSpecialist Operations said: "This must
OL,8,Fhave been really terrifying for the
OL,9,Fwoman who was in the passenger seat
OL,10,Fwhen the car got stolen.
OL,12,F"She is blind and has dementia, she
OL,13,Fwouldn't have known what was going on
OL,14,F` I can't even begin to imagine what
OL,15,Fwas going through her mind.
OL,17,F"I am proud of my officers, whose fast
OL,18,Fthinking and ability to remain calm in
OL,19,Fany given situation, meant we were
OL,20,Fable to bring the vehicle to a safe
OL,21,Fstop, and swiftly arrest Stephenson.
